article.description: — Jordan Davis had 22 points as Middle Tennessee defeated Covenant 76-57 on Saturday.
article.headline: Davis lifts Middle Tennessee past Covenant 76-57
article.linkText: Davis lifts Middle Tennessee past Covenant 76-57
article.story: MURFREESBORO, Tenn. -- — Jordan Davis had 22 points as Middle Tennessee defeated Covenant 76-57 on Saturday. Dontrell Shuler had 16 points for Middle Tennessee (2-3). Luke Touliatos had 12 points for the Scots. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
